CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

January 25, 2007

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2006-1609. Solon v. Mazala.

Cuyahoga App. No. 87055. This cause came on for further consideration of appellant’s motion to instruct the Clerk to scan previously filed documents. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
